<!-- ═══════════════ PROGRAMME HIGHLIGHTS ═══════════════ -->
<section class="section-pad">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow reveal">Retreat Programme</span>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal rd1">The <span class="text-red">Programme</span></h2>
    <p class="section-sub reveal rd2">Three days of purpose-driven sessions — faith, practical skills, and holiness — designed to strengthen young people and send them out for greater impact.</p>

    <div class="yw-grid">
    <div class="yw-card reveal rd1">
    <span class="yw-day-tag red-tag">Friday · Day 1</span>
    <h4>Arrival &amp; Alignment</h4>
    <p>Opening exhortation and prayer by <strong>Sis Christianah</strong>. Camp setup, dinner, then worship and intercessory prayer led by <strong>Sis Victoria &amp; Mr Michael</strong>. Night teaching sessions: The Gospel (Sis Josephine) and Discipleship (Bro Solomon), followed by a Christian movie night.</p>
    <a href="/activities" class="card-link">Full Schedule →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="yw-card yw-card-featured reveal rd2">
    <span class="yw-day-tag blue-tag">Saturday · Day 2</span>
    <h4>Equipping for Impact</h4>
    <p>Communication skills (<strong>Sis Victoria</strong>), soap making, Nigerian Tax Reform lecture (<strong>CSM Charles</strong>), Relationship Talks by <strong>Major Blessing Eboh</strong> and <strong>Major Sarah Oyedele (DDWM)</strong>, Tech skills (<strong>Mr Joshua Olatunde</strong>), and Moment of Truth reflections (<strong>Mrs Ntuk</strong>).</p>
    <a href="/activities" class="card-link">Full Schedule →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="yw-card reveal rd3">
    <span class="yw-day-tag gold-tag">Sunday · Day 3</span>
    <h4>Holiness Meeting</h4>
    <p>Sunday holiness service led by <strong>Sis Christianah</strong>. Worship by Sis Josephine, Bible reading by Sis Faith, testimonies by Bro Solomon, and the holiness message preached by <strong>Bro Michael</strong>. Closing prayer and benediction by the Commanding Officer.</p>
    <a href="/activities" class="card-link">Full Schedule →</a>
    </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

